            "body": "Hi [~busbey], thanks for raising this. How would this compare with the ongoing work at HADOOP-13070? Is your thinking that shading should be the/a mechanism for isolation for containers instead of the classloader isolation?\n\nNote that the classloader isolation already exists and folks have been using it to accomplish isolation. I think we may need to sort out what our story on this is for 3.0 going forward.",
